snippet.title: Djinn - The Forbidden Knowledge - Trailer
snippet.description:
#djinn #horror #indiegame 

Djinn - The Forbidden Knowledge is a thrilling, open-world horror adventure with a retro aesthetic. Immerse yourself in this unique story as an Arabian Princess, trapped in a realm that mirrors your deepest fears. As you navigate the twisted world, confront your enemies and unearth the dark secrets that lurk within. Can you overcome your demons and escape this nightmare, or will it consume you forever?

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2941750/Djinn__The_Forbidden_Knowledge

Epic: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/djinn-the-forbidden-knowledge-1f5924

Music: The Last One by World Music Official
